nodes.text: A store was located in the city Barons Hed, located on the moon Sulon. It was operated by a Human female merchant. After the arrival of the Dark Jedi Jerec, who briefly governed the city, the store became one of the few non-cantina establishments to have not shut its doors. The woman was once harassed by a pair of Gran bounty hunters. A supporter of the Rebel Alliance, the woman kept the store stocked with various kinds of weaponry, which were all located in a hidden room behind the main desk.
